reviewText: Tow movies on that disc for the price of one, very good deal. The first movie ( Deep tango) is full of everything regarding sex from A to Z., full nudity, oral, and complete sex course, beside the picture was very clear like they just made the movie Yesterday. and about the story it was so, so, Now the question was it worth the money; YES. And for the second movie (Young Secretaries) it was Ok no big deal, it has a better story, more locations, better acting, and direction, but it is not rated X, in our days I can rated R rating because of cutting some of the good parts, After all I consider what I paid for both movies reasonable price.
